{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"Window.performance","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/performance_property","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Performance_API\">Performance API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/performance_property\"><code>Performance_property</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ähnliche Seiten zu High Resolution Time</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMHighResTimeStamp\"><code>DOMHighResTimeStamp</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceEntry\"><code>PerformanceEntry</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceMark\"><code>PerformanceMark</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceMeasure\"><code>PerformanceMeasure</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceNavigation\"><code>PerformanceNavigation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming\"><code>PerformanceResourceTiming</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceTiming\"><code>PerformanceTiming</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Die Eigenschaft <strong><code>performance </code></strong>der&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a> Schnittstelle&nbsp; gibt ein <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Performance\"><code>Performance</code></a> Objekt zurück, welches benutzt werden kann, um Performanz-Informationen über das aktuelle Dokument zu sammeln. Sie dient als Bereitstellungspunkt für die&nbsp;Performance Timeline API, die High Resolution Time API, die&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigation_timing_API\">Navigation Timing API</a>, die&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/User_Timing_API\">User Timing API</a>, und die&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Resource_Timing_API\">Resource Timing API</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>performanceData</em> = window.performance;</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"wert","title":"Wert","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Ein <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Performance\"><code>Performance</code></a>-Objekt bietet Zugriff auf Performanz- und Timing-Informationen, die von den APIs, welche es offen legt, bereit gestellt werden.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/hr-time-1/#the-performance-interface\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">High Resolution Time<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'window.performance' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>Definiert die&nbsp;<code>now()</code> Methode.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browserkompabilität","title":"Browserkompabilität","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\"><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Wir konvertieren die Kompatibilitätsdaten in ein maschinenlesbares JSON Format</a></strong>.\n            Diese Kompatibilitätstabelle liegt noch im alten Format vor,\n            denn die darin enthaltenen Daten wurden noch nicht konvertiert.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Finde heraus wie du helfen kannst! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect4\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari (WebKit)</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Grundsätzliche Unterstützung</td>\n   <td>6.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/7\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2011-09-26.\">7.0</a> (7.0)</td>\n   <td>9.0</td>\n   <td>15.0</td>\n   <td>8</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Android Webview</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Phone</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Grundsätzliche Unterstützung</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td>7.0 (7.0)</td>\n   <td>9.0</td>\n   <td>15.0</td>\n   <td>9</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browserkompabilität","id":"browserkompabilität"}],"summary":"Die Eigenschaft performance der Window Schnittstelle  gibt ein Performance Objekt zurück, welches benutzt werden kann, um Performanz-Informationen über das aktuelle Dokument zu sammeln. Sie dient als Bereitstellungspunkt für die Performance Timeline API, die High Resolution Time API, die Navigation Timing API, die User Timing API, und die Resource Timing API.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"self.performance","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Window.performance","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Window.performance","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Window.performance","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Window.performance","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/performance_property","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/performance_property/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/performa